room_title: Escape room "The Ringmaster" by Dare 2 Escape in Orlando
room_address: 5041 W Irlo Bronson Memorial Hwy Kissimmee, FL 34746
room_description:
You have spent a magical day at the Circus, but as you are leaving, you notice a tent that you haven't explored. An elusive figure wearing a top hat and a red jacket approaches you and your friends, inviting you to come inside. The last thing you see is his scarred face before he hits you over the head with his wooden cane...
When you wake up, you glance at each other and make your way to the door, only to find it locked. Panic begins to set in as you realize that you have been caught by the elusive, mysterious Ringmaster who plans to turn you into his newest freaks for his traveling show. You have an hour to find a way to escape or it's curtains for everyone!
